org.polarsys.chess.chessmlprofile.Dependability.StateBased.MaintenanceMonitoring

Interface MMActivities

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ErrorDetection, FailureDetection, Repair, Replace
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ErrorDetectionImpl, FailureDetectionImpl, MMActivitiesImpl, RepairImpl, ReplaceImpl

    public interface MMActivities
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'MM Activities'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Base Activity
    • When
    • Duration
    • Prob Success
    • On Completion
    • On Successful Completion
    • On Failed Completion
    • Base Action
    See Also:
    MaintenanceMonitoringPackage.getMMActivities()
